{"tid":1578160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[喜訊] 正式拆大公報招牌！多謝連登仔女！","createTime":"2019-09-18T04:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T10:59:53.000Z","uid":295382,"like":103,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"c9722be20388bb99721dc5f80c0836caff12cdfc","tid":1578160,"uid":295382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T04:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NkrYoUr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNkrYoUr.jpg&h=0b7842b7&s={SIZE}\" />＿  <br />\n【軒尼詩道 僭建招牌跟進】<br />\n早前接獲市民投訴，懷疑豎立在灣仔國華大樓外牆的「大公報」招牌屬僭建，我們7月去信屋宇署要求調查。屋宇署下令招牌擁有人30日內清拆（即23/8），60日內（22/9前）完成。<br />\n據了解該招牌已僭建近8年，今天終於開始拆卸，雖然比原定限期遲了一點施工，今後路過的公眾人士將更安心安全了！<br />\n相關報導：<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065985&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=d38d0b41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065985&h=5020ec25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065985</a><br />\n<br />\n*感謝連登網民<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/susi.wanchai/photos/a.639318013226260/670110506813677/?type=3&amp;permPage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsusi.wanchai%2Fphotos%2Fa.639318013226260%2F670110506813677%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26permPage%3D1&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=4de76acb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/susi.wanchai/photos/a.639318013226260/670110506813677/?type=3&amp;permPage=1</a>"},{"pid":"6687a0749e2a271885d54d65f6f8b97799ade8c5","tid":1578160,"uid":117906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T04:56:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></