ces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好波"},{"pid":"5b866e1dde15d2e39ccd96e07537129cad53f834","tid":1578160,"uid":227699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:29:25.000Z","msg":"多謝1823專員"},{"pid":"843c7997e8ef4874b6cc93c61295d8055b641134","tid":1578160,"uid":288395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48b3e006a0e1168fbe0db802be86f5b55b61a9b","tid":1578160,"uid":75461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:23:54.000Z","msg":"BD今次做啱咗！"},{"pid":"538e9bee934ae79d3429ad96cdeea03698e55992","tid":1578160,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:53:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c1205060c3a48d5be0369b138435cb9c8dfd74f","tid":1578160,"uid":306925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"借貴寶地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1）警察<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">衰野太多，好難一張文宣講晒</span></span></strong><br />\n2）我地前線手足都開始<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反擊得勁D，反擊畫面</span></span></strong>又會被現在好落力打國際戰的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府拎黎大造文章，條片正好俾外國能更好地體諒我地</span></span></strong><br />\n3）更好利用一些<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">震撼畫面或者橋段，收籠外國人心</span></strong></span><br />\n4）微電影，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread</span></span></strong>我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣都塞條片的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"b0a7b82c11e31867844d1730c6bfe557002e8ea5","tid":1578160,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:01:40.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第五期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1</a><br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=5d8070bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"034801757998e7c211021555ce3916edf5465bf4","tid":1578160,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5f9bd2a1bb24d29ee513d9152838e0167138d4","tid":1578160,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"